STEP 1 — TAP
• Kid taps anywhere on the Flubber Coin screen
• Each tap = 1 Flubber Coin
• Soft sound + tiny bounce animation

STEP 2 — MILESTONE MOMENTS
• At 100 taps → sticker
• At 250 taps → color accent
• At 500 taps → accessory shop unlock
• At 1000 taps → bedroom + holiday scenes unlock

STEP 3 — COIN COUNTER
• Coin total always visible
• No timers, no streaks, no pressure

STEP 4 — SHOP ENTRY
• Kid taps the “Shop” button
• Categories appear: Accessories, Animations, Rooms, Holiday

STEP 5 — PREVIEW
• Tap item → preview on their Copilot avatar or room

STEP 6 — PURCHASE
• “Buy for ___ coins” button
• No real money, ever
• Instant equip + celebration animation

STEP 7 — CUSTOMIZE
• Kid returns to their Copilot bedroom
• Places items, changes outfits, swaps scenes
